<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #ffc107; color: #333; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .info { background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Subscription Cancelled</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{firstName}},</h2>
            <p>We're sorry to see you go. Your ClaudeOSaar subscription has been cancelled.</p>
            <div class="info">
                <h3>Important Information:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Access until: {{accessUntil}}</li>
                    <li>Data retention: 30 days after cancellation</li>
                    <li>You can reactivate anytime before {{accessUntil}}</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <p>We'd love to hear your feedback. Please reply to this email to let us know how we can improve.</p>
            <p>Thank you for being part of ClaudeOSaar.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>